Notes: This registers and controls the enemies requested by a CareTakerHunter. This object is usually linked to a CareTakerHunter using GeneratorId. Otherwise, it's useless on its own. The requested enemies can be attached to this object by setting their GeneratorId to this object's l_id. Supported enemies are Kuribo, TogeBegomanLauncher, BegomanLauncher and BegomanBabyLauncher. If a requested enemy is in this object's sensor range, it will notify the linked CareTakerHunter.

SW_A.Description: Activated after the request is fulfilled.
